Repasemos la lista juntos.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:05.800
Ven aquí.

00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:07.520
Yo me encargaré de ello.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:10.040
Su Alteza,

00:10:11.920 --> 00:10:13.240
Vamos a repasar allí.

00:10:13.536 --> 00:10:14.080
Venir.

00:10:14.080 --> 00:10:15.640
Este lado tiene una mejor vista.

00:10:15.640 --> 00:10:16.224
Apurarse.

00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:17.320
Vamos.

00:10:18.520 --> 00:10:19.400
Siéntate aquí.

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:21.920
Mirar,

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:23.320
Hemos preparado muchos artículos.

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:25.640
Sentarse.

00:10:31.880 --> 00:10:32.480
Suficiente.

00:10:33.720 --> 00:10:34.960
Esto es asunto de mujeres.

00:10:36.320 --> 00:10:37.640
No deberías quedarte aquí

00:10:40.400 --> 00:10:40.920
Excelente.

00:10:41.640 --> 00:10:43.160
Necesito hablar con Lady Hong.

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:44.520
Me despido.

00:10:44.800 --> 00:10:45.560
Su Alteza,

00:10:46.040 --> 00:10:47.680
De repente me siento mal.

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:49.280
Debo disculparme.

00:10:52.560 --> 00:10:53.240
¡Detener!

